{
  "stem": "11184.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wanted-- what did I want to be?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wanted to go to school, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know we couldn't afford.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And to, to-- I liked to type, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I thought, I'll be a typist--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--an office worker.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what I-- so in Germany, that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to school and learned how to type.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war, yeah, yeah, mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, very much so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The paper was every day in our house, the newspaper, the",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew what's going on with the German Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had neighbors that came-- they were thrown out from Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One-- in 1934, one family--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--came and lived downstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in 1938, the-- another family of theirs came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also they were, you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] emigrate-- not emigrated, but they were-- they were thrown out of--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Germany.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's put it this way, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents, they were always together, just not to leave family, very knit-- close.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister wanted to go to, to Russia, I mean, when the war broke out--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was already sitting with her luggage because she knew a young man that went to Russia-- Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came back to bring her-- his parents back to Russia and promised her that she's going to go with him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was so anxious to go, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the only one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She wanted to be in Russia, mostly, yeah, because-- away, away from--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Germany.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and he was postponing, postponing until the ghetto was closed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody could go out anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she, she couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wanted to be with his mother, or whoever.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
